# Python Environment

This project uses **uv** for dependency management, NOT conda.

## Running Python commands

Always use `uv run` to execute Python commands in the project virtualenv:

```bash
# ✅ Good
uv run python scripts/compare_em_convergence.py
uv run pytest tests/
uv run python -c "import normix; print(normix.__version__)"

# ❌ Bad - do NOT use conda
conda run -n normix python ...
conda activate normix && python ...
```

## Adding dependencies

```bash
uv add pandas
uv add --dev pytest
```
